      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm confused. A second ago you said the current Court was engaging in overreach and abandoning its duty, but now you're saying their approach is the \"only correct way\" to interpret the Constitution? You've completely flipped your position. Are you saying one of those legal philosophies is just fundamentally wrong?",
